fix(aws): dynamic import of @aws-sdk/client-sts to prevent startup crash

The static import at the top of whoami/defaultAction.ts caused Node to
fail with ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND at startup — even for `getdotenv -h` —
when @aws-sdk/client-sts is not installed. Since the SDK is an optional
peer dependency, the import must be deferred to the action handler so it
only resolves when the aws whoami command is actually invoked.
